data.title: Glasses & Eye Care in IA
data.meta_description: Eyemart Optical Outlet provides central Iowa & the Des Moines area with eyewear, eye care services, eye exams, eyeglasses, & more. Visit us today!
data.text:
Quality Glasses at

Competitive Prices

GLASSES AS LOW AS $49.50!

About Eyemart Optical Outlet

We’re why Iowa starts with “EYE”! Eyemart is a locally owned family business dedicated to providing you with eyewear for the most economical prices on the market. At Eyemart, our philosophy is that glasses should be affordable without sacrificing quality or style. We offer a large selection of designer frames to choose from — at closeout prices!

Eye Exams

At all our locations, our experienced eye doctors offer comprehensive eye exams. Get a thorough eye health screening and precise vision prescription today

Contact Lenses & Online Ordering

We carry a wide selection of top contact lens brands, and cater to your eye doctor’s recommendations. With our fast shipping and online ordering, you’ll never run out.

Six Convenient Locations in Central Iowa

Eyemart Optical Outlet has storefronts across central Iowa. You’re never far from the affordable, quality frames you deserve.

LOCALLY OWNED FAMILY BUSINESS

Providing You With Quality Glasses for the Best Price in the Market

Experienced, Friendly Doctors

Our team of independent doctors are highly trained, extremely dedicated, and bring years of experience to each of our practices. When you come to Eyemart for a comprehensive eye exam, your optometrist will take the time to get to know you and learn about your unique eyes. We provide a personalized experience and a precise prescription to give you your best vision.

TESTIMONIALS

What People are Saying

Great Quality & Price

“I have been buying my glasses from Eyemart Optical for many years now. I’ve always been satisfied with the quality and and prices! Sonya delivers the best customer service. Over the years she has gotten to know my style and I can always expect honest and objective feedback from her.”

-J.H.

Amazing Prices

“The ladies at Eyemart Optical Outlet are so helpful and the prices are amazing! I have purchased 8 pairs of glasses from them and I will continue to do business with them.

-S.A.

Great Selection of Frames

“I had a great experience at Eyemart Optical Outlet! All staff members were friendly and helpful. We were offered various payment options such as pay for half now and pay for the other half later. Great selection of frames and fair cost.”

-J.B.

Couldn't Be More Pleased

“The Optometrist that I had the pleasure of meeting and all of the staff were more than helpful and attentive. I couldn’t be more pleased with my new glasses and would highly recommend Eyemart Optical Outlet to anyone looking for quality glasses and full attention to detail.”

-A.P.
